OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FITV News' reporter Philip Sime reports
OL,7,Fon the concern caused by these attacks.
OL,9,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,10,Finsisted there is no place for race-
OL,11,Fbased or faith-based violence in the
OL,12,Fcountry after receiving a police
OL,13,Fbriefing on a series of suspected anti-
OL,14,FMuslim attacks in Edinburgh.
OL,16,FSwinney was updated on the
OL,17,Finvestigation into Friday's incidents
OL,18,Fby Police Scotland Assistant Chief
OL,19,FConstable Catriona Paton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
