OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FPolice Scotland has charged a 36-year-
OL,7,Fold man in connection with attacks
OL,8,Fthat Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fsaid appeared to be motivated by "anti-
OL,10,FMuslim hatred".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FCounter-terrorism officers were
OL,18,Fbrought in to investigate the attacks
OL,19,Facross the city which left five people
OL,20,Finjured.
