OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FThe force said on Saturday a white
OL,7,FScottish man had been arrested.
OL,9,FIt said late on Saturday night: "A 36-
OL,10,Fyear-old man has been charged in
OL,11,Fconnection with a number of incidents
OL,12,Fwhich took place in Edinburgh on
OL,13,FFriday, 19 June, 2026.
OL,15,F"A report has been submitted to the
OL,16,Fprocurator fiscal, and the individual
OL,17,Fwill appear at court in due course."
OL,26,@qD@aOUwD@AOUyD@dO]
