OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FFootage posted online showed a bare-
OL,7,Fchested white man roaming the streets
OL,8,Fof Edinburgh with a large weapon,
OL,9,Fwhile another clip seemed to show a
OL,10,Fman battering the door of a pizzeria.
OL,12,FPolice closed off Leith Walk on Friday
OL,13,Fevening as the incidents unfolded and
OL,14,Fanother video appeared to show a
OL,15,Ftopless man on the ground shouting
OL,16,Fthat he is "protecting the country" as
OL,17,Fhe is held by an officer.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@cO]
