OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FThey were told about the support being
OL,7,Fprovided to those who were directly
OL,8,Fimpacted by the attacks and what
OL,9,Factions are being taken to offer
OL,10,Freassurance to members of Scotland's
OL,11,FMuslim community.
OL,13,FSwinney will meet with members of the
OL,14,FMuslim community on Monday.
OL,16,F"There is no place for race-based or
OL,17,Ffaith-based violence in Scotland,"
OL,18,Fsaid the First Minister.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
