OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,F"The suspect appears to be motivated
OL,7,Fby anti-Muslim hatred. I will not
OL,8,Ftolerate this ` he will face the full
OL,9,Fforce of the law.
OL,11,F"My thoughts are with those who are
OL,12,Finjured and I thank the police and the
OL,13,Femergency services for their response."
OL,15,FOfficers were called to a report of an
OL,16,Fincident in the Sighthill area of the
OL,17,Fcity, where two men were injured, at
OL,18,Faround 8.50pm on Friday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@gO]
