OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FPolice said they then received reports
OL,7,Fabout incidents around retailers
OL,8,Facross the west and north of the city.
OL,10,FThe force said that during this period
OL,11,Fthree other men were allegedly
OL,12,Fattacked in the Telford Road and Leith
OL,13,FWalk area.
OL,15,FPolice said that five men ` two aged
OL,16,F22, and others aged 24, 27, and 39 `
OL,17,Fsustained a range of injuries. Three
OL,18,Fneeded hospital treatment, although
OL,19,Fnone of the injuries are life-
OL,20,Fthreatening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
