OL,3,CPeople must stand united in condemning
OL,4,CEdinburgh attacks, says John Swinney
OL,6,FSeveral of the victims are Muslim,
OL,7,Faccording to the Muslim Engagement and
OL,8,FDevelopment (Mend) organisation. It is
OL,9,Funderstood two of the incidents
OL,10,Fhappened near Broomhouse Mosque in the
OL,11,Fwest of Edinburgh.
OL,13,FPolice said a 36-year-old man was
OL,14,Fdetained at around 9.30pm on Friday.
OL,15,FThe Scottish Association of Mosques
OL,16,Fsaid it was "deeply concerned".
OL,18,FPolice are appealing to anyone with
OL,19,Finformation that could assist with
OL,20,Finquiries to upload it using an online
OL,21,Fform.
